						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Process
					p Drio Duo partnered with me to design and develop the new website. I created high-fidelity mockups in Figma and built a responsive WordPress site with a focus on usability, accessibility, and clear content organization. The redesign centered on presenting training opportunities, union expertise, and contractor support in a way that industry professionals could easily navigate.
					h6
						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Outcome
					p The new site offers a modern design that aligns with the partnershipâ€™s brand and improves accessibility, navigation, and visibility of programs and resources.
						
